&lt;p&gt;Here the divorce willing couples were imprisoned - with only one bed, one table, one plate, one cup, one spoon, etc. They were so long held there until they wanted to reverse their separation. The legend says: in the 400 years the divorce house was used, there should have been alleged only one divorce !!! ;-D&lt;/p&gt;

